This is a darkened theater, where the aquarium would show various educational films.  Several rows of low benches face a screen on the western wall; an aperture set high in the eastern wall allows a projector to project movies onto the screen.

A door leads back out to the main aquarium to the west; a ladder against the eastern wall leads up to the AV/projection room.
