The cliff terminates at a smooth rocky plateau, dotted with scrubby patches of withered sea grass.  A monstrous lighthouse, white paint peeling to reveal dirty gray stone, erupts from the broken ground, thrusting up into the darkened sky.  The light in its tower is dim.  You notice a moss-covered wooden door set into the base of the lighthouse.
> use combination lock

> use combination lock
The code to open the padlock is some random combination of four numbers.  What combination do you enter?
